Package application.model

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CashotSystem
    CashotSystem class serves as our cental hub and contains all controllers, and methods to update our employees and items
    Employee
    Employee class represents a Employee object which has an employeeName,userName,employeePassword,ID,admin,trainiee,cashier, and an arrayList.
    Item
    The Item class holds data for the creation of an item and its respective name, price, row, and column
    Order
    The Order class holds the information for price totals, the employee, date, time, and IDs
    Receipt
    The Receipt class holds information for receipts such as the date, time, update log, and print of its creation
